Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.95,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}只是想輕快地起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.80,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}又要從頭再來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.03,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}加劇的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.00,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}用玩笑掩蓋黑暗
